        "headerType": "like-h2",
        "content": "<p>Ecommerce digital transformation can be a challenge for non-digitally savvy manufacturers, wholesalers, and distributors. For companies in the early stage&nbsp;of digital adoption, digital transformation involves getting control of the customer experience and leveraging customer insights.</p>\n\n<p>Avoid common mistakes by creating a roadmap for ecommerce that includes a strategic&nbsp;approach&nbsp;to organizational process and careful technology selection.&nbsp;</p>\n",
